WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:02.405
♪ Crashing through
the crowded halls ♪

00:02.429 --> 00:03.655
♪ Dodging girls
like ping pong balls ♪

00:03.679 --> 00:06.195
♪ Just to reach
the bathroom on time ♪

00:06.265 --> 00:07.484
♪ Leaping over laundry piles ♪

00:07.593 --> 00:08.874
♪ Diapers you can
smell for miles ♪

00:08.898 --> 00:12.710
♪ Guy's gotta do
what he can to survive ♪

00:12.773 --> 00:14.998
♪ In the Loud House,
in the Loud House ♪

00:15.037 --> 00:16.757
♪ Duck, dodge, push and shove ♪

00:16.851 --> 00:17.983
♪ This is how we show our love ♪

00:18.007 --> 00:20.529
♪ In the Loud House,
in the Loud House ♪

00:20.554 --> 00:21.851
♪ One boy and ten girls ♪

00:21.890 --> 00:23.726
♪ Wouldn't trade it
for the world ♪

00:23.791 --> 00:26.976
♪ Loud! Loud! Loud! ♪

00:27.031 --> 00:29.742
♪ Loud House! ♪♪
Boo boo.
